<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 12:52:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰萨博 340 机载预警雷达飞机被发现在该国上空运行</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-saab-340-airborne-early-warning-radar-plane-spotted-operating-over-the-country</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在保持低调后，一段视频出现，显然显示一架萨博 340 预警和控制飞机在乌克兰上空飞行。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-saab-340-airborne-early-warning-radar-plane-spotted-operating-over-the-country"&gt;乌克兰萨博 340 机载预警雷达飞机被发现在该国上空运行，该飞机&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 22:57:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-saab-340-airborne-early-warning-radar-plane-spotted-operating-over-the-country</guid></item><item><title>美国“拳师”号两栖攻击舰现正驶往中东（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/uss-boxer-the-second-amphibious-assault-ship-now-heading-to-middle-east</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着两个两栖战斗群前往中东，越来越多的人猜测美国将试图夺取伊朗的战略哈格岛。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/uss-boxer-the-second-amphibious-assault-ship-now-heading-to-middle-east"&gt;美国海军拳师号第二两栖攻击舰正在前往中东（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 22:26:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/uss-boxer-the-second-amphibious-assault-ship-now-heading-to-middle-east</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-184</link><description>&lt;p&gt;掩体时间，宝贝！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-184"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 22:21:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-184</guid></item><item><title>前中央司令部指挥官表示，在伊朗地面上行动可能会带来什么后果</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commander-on-what-u-s-boots-on-the-ground-in-iran-could-entail</link><description>&lt;p&gt;约瑟夫·沃特尔提供了有关确保伊朗铀矿安全、夺取哈格岛、减少导弹拦截器库存以及“史诗之怒”将持续多久的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commander-on-what-u-s-boots-on-the-ground-in-iran-could-entail"&gt;据前中央司令部司令称，伊朗地面上的靴子可能会带来什么帖子&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 21:33:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commander-on-what-u-s-boots-on-the-ground-in-iran-could-entail</guid></item><item><title>前中央司令部司令对霍尔木兹海峡局势的坦率看法</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commanders-candid-take-on-the-situation-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;退役陆军将军约瑟夫·沃特尔对如何从伊朗手中夺回霍尔木兹海峡提出了独特的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commanders-candid-take-on-the-situation-in-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;前中央司令部指挥官对霍尔木兹海峡局势的坦率看法&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 22:13:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commanders-candid-take-on-the-situation-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>印度加入欧洲战斗机计划绝非易事</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/india-joining-one-of-europes-fighter-programs-is-anything-but-easy</link><description>&lt;p&gt;印度迫切需要新型战斗机，但欧洲的下一代战斗机可能不是答案。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/india-joining-one-of-europes-fighter-programs-is-anything-but-easy"&gt;印度加入欧洲战斗机计划绝非易事&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 20:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/india-joining-one-of-europes-fighter-programs-is-anything-but-easy</guid></item><item><title>美国空军 F-35 据称被伊朗炮火击中后紧急迫降</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-f-35-makes-emergency-landing-after-allegedly-being-hit-by-iranian-fire</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这架 F-35 在伊朗上空执行战斗任务时被迫转向美国空军基地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;美国空军 F-35 据称被伊朗&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;火力&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-f-35-makes-emergency-landing-after-allegedly-being-hit-by-iranian-fire"&gt;击中后紧急迫降&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 17:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-f-35-makes-emergency-landing-after-allegedly-being-hit-by-iranian-fire</guid></item><item><title>A-10疣猪正在霍尔木兹海峡搜寻伊朗船只</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-prowling-for-iranian-boats-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;A-10 战斗机正在执行一项鲜为人知的任务，他们已经训练了几十年，在海峡追捕伊朗快速攻击艇和布雷层。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-prowling-for-iranian-boats-in-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;A-10 疣猪在霍尔木兹海峡搜寻伊朗船只&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 16:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-prowling-for-iranian-boats-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>RQ-180 秘密隐形无人机似乎已紧急降落在希腊空军基地（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base</link><description>&lt;p&gt;希腊的观察者特别仔细地观察到了一架似乎特别神秘的无人机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; RQ-180 秘密隐形无人机似乎在希腊&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;空军&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base"&gt;基地紧急着陆（更新）&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的能源基础设施现已列入目标清单（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list</link><description>&lt;p&gt;南帕尔斯气田的袭击使伊朗的能源生产成为焦点，而这对伊朗政府的资金至关重要。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list"&gt;伊朗的能源基础设施现已列入目标清单（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 22:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list</guid></item></channel></rss>